Five Rings<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ushelrabbi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shelrabbi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 148<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/21/02 4:28:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1691.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hate building (without shissar/serubane)</span><hr size=1> Proximity ALWAYS matters to aggro. A mob rooted by a player will cast at whoever is highest on the hate list and hit whoever is physically closest. Test it out on a orc shaman or some other caster type.<br>
