<br>
So, in my observations aggro is heavily influenced by proximity, but not bound by the &quot;attack closest&quot; rules as if was magically rooted by a player. Also, they will turn to those with low health and melee them to death. <p><BR>Besrikarle Armiger`Yasdnil<BR>
